{"tid":1675810,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"和平既連登仔又會衝出黎話唔好裝修譚仔架啦","createTime":"2019-10-26T06:20:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T14:44:41.000Z","uid":132587,"like":7,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"df13ef45f9db382a8baf4e3ab5797a913c36d2fc","tid":1675810,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T06:20:15.000Z","msg":"之前中資次次比人裝修都一大班人走出黎<br />\n小米民企黎架唔好搞 中資黎講算黃架啦<br />\n又話唔好無差別裝修 唔好搞三中商 唔好搞銀行<br />\n<br />\n到旺角小米宣佈無限期暫停營業<br />\n又一大班勝利球迷出黎話 邊個話裝修無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到今次譚仔啦 香港人命脈<br />\n睇到大部份留言 唔好話裝修<br />\n連罷食都唔話唔洗<br />\n又幫人開脫話 會唔會比人借刀 會唔會係d員工自己貼 睇定d先 唔好對號入座<br />\n仲話香港人反抗 算撚數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你下次係街比狗鬧 不如都話睇定d先 唔好對號入座 未必係話緊我地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你唔自認曱甴 但明眼人都知佢地話緊邊d人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果呢d少少野比人恰到上頸都幫人開脫 你地下世做辣肉墨演比人食好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"693306695235bd4f7c489e643fbcc9d9795c66b4","tid":1675810,"uid":276916,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T06:21:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"894d40b422f71d170f2a6df4c81bf94e14cc37f3","tid":1675810,"uid":3358,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T06:24:56.000Z","msg":"人地講句唔岩聽說話就要裝修人<br />\n你當自己係咩人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衰撚過畜牲"},{"pid":"8a60f722c4437c3c2ba48d266dc028559ba18346","tid":1675810,"uid":30040,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T06:25:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">從來唔認為示威者係曱甴， 唔需要自我代